Loaded packages

loaded_packages.Rd

Loaded packages

loaded_packages(pkg, verbose = TRUE)

Arguments

pkg

A package name.
verbose

Whether to print messages.

Details

It loads package pkg in a new R session and collects which other packages are loaded from sessionInfo.

Value

A data frame.

Examples

loaded_packages("ComplexHeatmap")
